name: Tom Cruise
summary: The 2024 Paris Olympics concluded with an unforgettable grand finale, where Hollywood superstar Tom Cruise emerged as a surprise guest. Cruise captivated the audience with a daring skydiving stunt, descending from the stadium roof and delivering the Olympic flag to Los Angeles, the host city of the 2028 Games. The actor's heroic act symbolized the passing of the torch and the anticipation for the upcoming event. The media hailed Cruise's performance as an "epic stunt," praising his bold execution and the resounding impact it had on the closing ceremony. Cruise's appearance not only highlighted the upcoming Olympics but also signaled a change from traditional closing ceremonies, adding a touch of Hollywood glamor to the sporting spectacle.
